OL,3,C'Humbling' to be voice of mother and
OL,4,Cbaby home victims and survivors
OL,6,FPaul McClarey wasn't even three weeks
OL,7,Fold when he was taken from his
OL,8,Fmother's arms. Someone he would never
OL,9,Fget to know.
OL,11,FHis mother was a young girl from
OL,12,FLondonderry, who was only 18 years old
OL,13,Fand "found herself pregnant, not
OL,14,Fmarried".
OL,16,FShe was sent to Marianville mother and
OL,17,Fbaby institution on the Ormeau Road in
OL,18,FBelfast, where Paul was taken from her
OL,19,Fat 18 days old, moved into the care
OL,20,Fsystem, boarded out and adopted at six
OL,21,Fand a half years old.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
