OL,3,C'Humbling' to be voice of mother and
OL,4,Cbaby home victims and survivors
OL,6,FPaul was just one of thousands of
OL,7,Fchildren taken as their mothers were
OL,8,Fforced into hard labour.
OL,10,FOn Tuesday, a landmark report found
OL,11,Fthat admissions to mother and baby
OL,12,Fhomes in Northern Ireland were
OL,13,Festimated to be 2,000 higher than
OL,14,Ffirst thought.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1783667970
OL,3,C'Humbling' to be voice of mother and
OL,4,Cbaby home victims and survivors
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the co-chairs of the Truth
OL,7,FRecovery Independent Panel found that
OL,8,F"human rights abuses, degrading
OL,9,Ftreatment, and forced separation of
OL,10,Ffamilies are recurring and frequent"
OL,11,Fin evidence from survivors of the
OL,12,Fhomes.
OL,14,FOver 12,000 women in Northern Ireland
OL,15,Fare estimated to have been admitted to
OL,16,Fmother and baby homes and over 3,700
OL,17,Fto Magdalene Laundries.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1783667970
OL,3,C'Humbling' to be voice of mother and
OL,4,Cbaby home victims and survivors
OL,6,FIt's their stories which are compiled
OL,7,Fin the extensive and lengthy report
OL,8,Fthat will now be taken forward in a
OL,9,Ffuture public inquiry.
OL,11,FPaul told UTV: "Years later, when I
OL,12,Fwas 22 years old, I got some
OL,13,Finformation, tried to trace her. But
OL,14,Funfortunately, by the time I had got
OL,15,Fto her address, she had died ten years
OL,16,Fearlier.
OL,18,F"She died when she was 29 years old.
OL,19,FSo, I will never see her again."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1783667970
OL,3,C'Humbling' to be voice of mother and
OL,4,Cbaby home victims and survivors
OL,6,F"I think as a child, I always knew I
OL,7,Fwas in the wrong place. There was
OL,8,Fsomething inside of me that knew I
OL,9,Fdidn't belong here.
OL,11,F"There's a narrative that 'we'll take
OL,12,Fthese babies and give them a good
OL,13,Fhome, and you know, a good middle-
OL,14,Fclass upbringing, and they'll have a
OL,15,Fgood life,' but for many of us, that
OL,16,Fwas far from the truth."
OL,18,FPaul said that the discovery of his
OL,19,Fmother's death and the trauma took
OL,20,Ftime to come to terms with.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1783667970
OL,3,C'Humbling' to be voice of mother and
OL,4,Cbaby home victims and survivors
OL,6,F"I could have had a life with her, but
OL,7,Fthat life was taken away from me.
OL,9,F"The very people that should have
OL,10,Flooked after me and my mother, and
OL,11,Fthousands of other vulnerable people
OL,12,Fat their time of need, they failed us
OL,13,Fbadly."
OL,15,FHe said being part of the panel was a
OL,16,F"privilege" and "humbling" experience.
OL,18,F"It's been the privilege of my life to
OL,19,Frepresent fellow victims and survivors.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@KO]xD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1783667970
OL,3,C'Humbling' to be voice of mother and
OL,4,Cbaby home victims and survivors
OL,6,F"I'd like to pay tribute to the 238
OL,7,Fvictims and survivors who have come
OL,8,Fforward and shared their lived
OL,9,Fexperience with the panel.
OL,11,F"Many of them for the first time.
OL,12,FThey've never spoken about this to
OL,13,Fanybody, and they may never speak
OL,14,Fabout it again.
OL,16,F"To be able to represent their voices
OL,17,Fand be their voice on the panel has
OL,18,Fbeen a humbling experience.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1783667970
OL,3,C'Humbling' to be voice of mother and
OL,4,Cbaby home victims and survivors
OL,6,F"I hope when they read this report,
OL,7,Fthey will recognise themselves in
OL,8,Fevery single page, because this is for
OL,9,Fthem. This is their day."
OL,11,FWhen exactly a public inquiry will
OL,12,Fbegin is not yet known, but the
OL,13,FExecutive has confirmed it will happen.
OL,15,FIt said it will now carefully consider
OL,16,Fthe findings, and a coordinated
OL,17,Fresponse will be provided in due
OL,18,Fcourse.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
